# NOTE: these Python build dirs are root-anchored on purpose. An unanchored
# `lib/` also matched frontend/src/lib/ and silently un-tracked all shared
# frontend code (stores, components) — every clone built broken. Do not
# un-anchor these.
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg
